    "name": "扑克大乱斗",
    "steam_appid": 3307030,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《扑克大乱斗》是一款休闲风格的自走棋策略类游戏，在其中玩家将扮演棋手，在由扑克牌幻化成英雄的世界中排兵布阵，运筹帷幄，最终在竞技场中获取最高荣誉——竞技场冠冕。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307030/extras/7c5c688bfdea6e65a3a33fe3f3788503.avif?t=1769743095\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307030/extras_big/7c5c688bfdea6e65a3a33fe3f3788503.avif?t=1769743095 width=800 height=258 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扑克牌英雄</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一张扑克牌都对应一位独特的英雄，拥有自己独特的形象与能力，你可以在战斗中消耗金币招募他们为你而战！三个相同的英雄即可升星变得更强，还有神秘而又强大的大小王等待你的招募！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307030/extras/a73a68be03862e3c29ee7069dd34b563.avif?t=1769743095\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307030/extras_big/a73a68be03862e3c29ee7069dd34b563.avif?t=1769743095 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >组成牌型，提升你的队伍能力</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当你的队伍中的英雄满足了某一个牌型的激活条件时，该牌型就会激活并提供对应增益给激活该牌型的所有英雄，合理构建你的队伍可以同时激活多个牌型；全部花色组成的同花顺，四张相同卡牌的炸弹，或者只有大小王才可以组成的特殊牌型，尽待你的探索；</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307030/extras/d1e77959bdc861e3e97d6c17230828d9.avif?t=1769743095\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307030/extras_big/d1e77959bdc861e3e97d6c17230828d9.avif?t=1769743095 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择闪卡，获取强大的特殊效果</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每隔几个回合，你就可以从三张闪卡中选择一张激活，激活的闪卡会在本局游戏中永久生效，是选择简单有效的属性加成还是增加金币的经济投资，是选择特殊阵容需要的复杂效果还是能够改变玩法的强大效果，耐心思考，做出自己的策略选择吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307030/extras/d0161bc9e25a5588c608553f676c5b25.avif?t=1769743095\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307030/extras_big/d0161bc9e25a5588c608553f676c5b25.avif?t=1769743095 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 抽取奖励，获得独特装饰</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >消耗货币即可在抽卡界面抽取独特的道具奖励，不仅可以获得各种生动有趣的表情让你在战斗中表达心情，还可以获取稀有的棋手或者棋盘皮肤让你的角色与场地变得与众不同！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307030/extras/bca90503c1c38b3f624616f4ddbe0a22.avif?t=1769743095\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3307030/extras_big/bca90503c1c38b3f624616f4ddbe0a22.avif?t=1769743095 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
